1
00:01:58,759 --> 00:01:59,320
Brother,

2
00:01:59,640 --> 00:02:00,640
this is too artsy.

3
00:02:01,600 --> 00:02:03,080
It won't sell at all.

4
00:02:03,920 --> 00:02:05,760
Do you know how many people

5
00:02:05,760 --> 00:02:07,560
have switched to making bubblegum pop?

6
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:08,960
It's quick cash.

7
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:10,850
Then find someone else.

8
00:02:11,720 --> 00:02:12,960
Songs without an audience

9
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:14,560
are meaningless to produce.

10
00:02:14,600 --> 00:02:16,320
You know this better than I do.

11
00:02:51,720 --> 00:02:52,440
How is it?

12
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:56,480
Not bad. He has some talent.

13
00:02:56,840 --> 00:02:57,480
Really?

14
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:58,720
Qiuqiu,

15
00:02:59,200 --> 00:03:00,200
what do you think?

16
00:03:00,880 --> 00:03:01,400
Okay.

17
00:03:01,600 --> 00:03:02,200
I agree.

18
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:05,000
We just need to get there

19
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:06,600
ten minutes early that day.

20
00:03:08,920 --> 00:03:09,850
Your mom is back.

21
00:03:11,040 --> 00:03:11,680
Hurry.

22
00:03:12,360 --> 00:03:13,320
Cover for me, quick.

23
00:03:13,320 --> 00:03:13,960
Okay.

24
00:03:21,079 --> 00:03:21,960
Hello, Uncle, Auntie.

25
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:22,840
Hello, Qiuqiu.

26
00:03:22,920 --> 00:03:24,560
Qiuqiu, you haven't been here in a while.

27
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:25,560
Why are you alone?

28
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:26,940
Where is that boy Anan?

29
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:28,440
He'll be down in a second.

30
00:03:28,440 --> 00:03:29,280
Coming.

31
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:32,240
Coming.

32
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,280
Mom, Dad,

33
00:03:33,600 --> 00:03:34,800
this is Mr. Liu.

34
00:03:37,040 --> 00:03:38,960
We're taking Qiuqiu home.

35
00:03:39,120 --> 00:03:40,280
It's not safe for her at night.

36
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:41,160
Goodbye, Uncle, Auntie.

37
00:03:41,160 --> 00:03:41,880
Bye, Mom, Dad. Okay.

38
00:03:41,880 --> 00:03:42,480
Bye.

39
00:03:42,480 --> 00:03:43,360
Get some rest.

40
00:03:43,520 --> 00:03:44,240
Okay.

41
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:55,120
This is the last time I cover for you.

42
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:56,520
Nine tomorrow morning.

43
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:57,320
Don't be late.

44
00:04:02,640 --> 00:04:03,720
Great!

45
00:04:03,880 --> 00:04:04,640
She said yes!

46
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:06,680
Yes!

47
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:08,800
It's not like she accepted your proposal.

48
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:10,060
Why are you so excited?

49
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:11,040
My band has you,

50
00:04:11,200 --> 00:04:11,800
my idol,

51
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:12,880
me, and Qiuqiu,

52
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:14,400
Lincang's number one drummer.

53
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:15,640
We will definitely win the competition.

54
00:04:15,640 --> 00:04:15,960
Yes.

55
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:17,320
I am so happy.

56
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:20,360
Tell me first.

57
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:22,920
How did I become Mr. Liu?

58
00:04:25,080 --> 00:04:26,080
I was too anxious.

59
00:04:26,280 --> 00:04:27,520
I will find a chance

60
00:04:27,520 --> 00:04:28,720
to explain properly.

61
00:04:44,280 --> 00:04:46,210
Isn't this the wall from the photo?

62
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:49,360
Saimeng.

63
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:50,760
Saimeng.

64
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:51,600
Saimeng,

65
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:52,440
are you home?

66
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:56,760
Anan.

67
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:57,640
Qiuqiu,

68
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:59,000
what brings you here?

69
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:01,130
Brother, I brought a friend to see you.

70
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:07,760
My zither.

71
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:10,360
Hello, I'm Liu Ma.

72
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:11,610
My father is Liu Niu.

73
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:13,760
I have an IOU here.

74
00:05:13,960 --> 00:05:14,480
And...

75
00:05:14,760 --> 00:05:15,690
This is Yanwang.

76
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:16,720
Is he your father?

77
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:20,160
My father is named Yanwang.

78
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:21,080
I'm sorry.

79
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:39,080
Look at the money. Here.

80
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:42,250
Then how can you prove this IOU is real?

81
00:05:43,680 --> 00:05:44,560
How can I prove it?

82
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:45,960
It just... it is real.

83
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:50,320
100,000 isn't a small amount.

84
00:05:50,760 --> 00:05:52,440
What if you just found this IOU somewhere?

85
00:05:52,440 --> 00:05:53,040
I didn't.

86
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:57,880
Saimeng, in the photo of Liuma's father,

87
00:05:57,880 --> 00:05:59,320
there was a wooden drum with a bull horn totem.

88
00:05:59,320 --> 00:06:01,720
Didn't your family use to make those drums?

89
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:07,370
Let me see the photo.

90
00:06:08,480 --> 00:06:09,640
I lost the photo.

91
00:06:09,840 --> 00:06:11,120
But this IOU is real.

92
00:06:11,280 --> 00:06:12,920
Brother, he really has been looking for you for a long time.

93
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:13,680
I'm sorry.

94
00:06:14,400 --> 00:06:16,200
I can't trust you just like that.

95
00:06:16,840 --> 00:06:18,080
And about you breaking my instrument,

96
00:06:18,080 --> 00:06:20,340
I haven't even settled that with you yet.

97
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:36,960
How did it go?

98
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:39,159
It's been too long.

99
00:06:39,159 --> 00:06:41,090
We probably won't find the wallet.

100
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:44,200
We can go to Wazhai to find Aye.

101
00:06:44,200 --> 00:06:45,480
He is the headman of the village.

102
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:47,340
He must remember such a big event.

103
00:06:47,880 --> 00:06:50,000
Do you have other photos of your dad?

104
00:06:50,159 --> 00:06:52,000
We can take the photos to find him.

105
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:52,800
Other photos?

106
00:06:52,880 --> 00:06:53,680
That's right.

107
00:06:53,800 --> 00:06:55,080
If Aye can prove it,

108
00:06:55,200 --> 00:06:56,400
Saimeng will definitely believe it.

109
00:06:56,400 --> 00:06:57,720
Let's go to the village now.

110
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:58,480
Take care.

111
00:07:02,280 --> 00:07:02,960
Grandpa.

112
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:04,400
Grandpa.

113
00:07:07,520 --> 00:07:09,120
Grandpa, please have a seat.

114
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:10,960
We have something urgent to ask.

115
00:07:10,960 --> 00:07:11,800
Please think back.

116
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:13,040
During the locust plague of 1999,

117
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:14,500
did an outsider come here?

118
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,000
An outsider?

119
00:07:17,080 --> 00:07:18,280
Someone named Liu Niu

120
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:21,220
borrowed 100,000 from Saimeng's father, Yanwang.

121
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:22,440
Could it be

122
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:24,760
that outsider who helped us

123
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:26,680
redeem the ancient tree?

124
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:31,240
During that plague,

125
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:32,760
Yanwang

126
00:07:33,240 --> 00:07:36,400
rescued an outsider who was lost in the mountains.

127
00:07:37,640 --> 00:07:39,200
But not long after,

128
00:07:39,640 --> 00:07:40,770
this out-of-towner

129
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:43,400
brought back a lot of money

130
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:45,460
and redeemed the Ancestral Tree.

131
00:07:46,159 --> 00:07:47,220
What are you doing?

132
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:48,620
Put the money away now.

133
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:49,440
Brother,

134
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:50,800
if you hadn't saved me on the tea mountain back then,

135
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:52,080
I would have died there long ago.

136
00:07:52,080 --> 00:07:52,880
You must take this money.

137
00:07:52,880 --> 00:07:55,680
If you keep this up, don't come into my house again.

138
00:07:59,320 --> 00:08:01,320
Ever since I arrived at the village,

139
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:03,620
everyone has treated me with their best.

140
00:08:03,840 --> 00:08:05,360
I'm well aware of that.

141
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:08,080
I owe you my life,

142
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:10,320
and I owe the village one too.

143
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:12,730
I'll redeem the Ancestral Tree

144
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:14,620
to repay the kindness.

145
00:08:15,120 --> 00:08:17,280
I didn't save you for your money.

146
00:08:20,520 --> 00:08:21,780
Then I'll write an IOU.

147
00:08:23,440 --> 00:08:24,840
Consider it a loan to you.

148
00:08:29,280 --> 00:08:31,140
Then you have to write it clearly.

149
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:32,280
It is a loan.

150
00:08:41,760 --> 00:08:42,820
Let's take a photo.

151
00:08:47,920 --> 00:08:49,980
My dad only told me he came to Lincang,

152
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:51,440
but I didn't know

153
00:08:51,920 --> 00:08:53,840
he went through so much here.
